{"tid":194254,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"城市科大「爆乳姊妹」腰瘦長腿神基因","createTime":"2017-04-10T00:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T02:26:39.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7eefebc6add7e09791dd1c1f6ea1608c0ce343ca","tid":194254,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2443/d2443365.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2443%2Fd2443365.jpg&h=a4fb6545&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲城市科技大學高紫寧（左圖左與右圖）和姊姊高紫安。（圖／校盟影業提供）<br />\n<br />\n記者許逸群／台北報導<br />\n<br />\n藝人「珍珍」無尊日前主持校盟影業之《校花點點名》，前往北投的台北城市科技大學，尋找神似南韓性感DJ SODA的校花高紫寧。不僅如此，到場後得知高紫寧的姊姊高紫安也非省油的燈，兩人都是ptt表特版常客，讓人不禁讚嘆果然一家都是神基因。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2443/d2443366.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2443%2Fd2443366.jpg&h=2a7462a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲高紫寧不僅身材好，且運動細胞與體能也相當不錯。（圖／校盟影業提供）<br />\n<br />\n同學形容高紫寧「皮膚白淨、眼睛大大、腰很細、胸部很大，男生看到都會忍不住要line」，同時更有近20名追求者，在校人氣不在話下。19歲的高紫寧擁有人人稱羨的好身材，纖細的小蠻腰配上性感的馬甲線；姊姊高紫安則有性感的小貓眼加上傲人上圍，172公分的她擁有107公分的長腿，167公分的妹妹也有100公分的長腿。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2443/d2443364.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2443%2Fd2443364.jpg&h=685165db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲高紫寧（右）與姊姊高紫安都有雙傲人長腿。（圖／校盟影業提供）<br />\n<br />\n高紫寧追求者眾多，在路上被搭訕已習以為常，但卻與姊姊高紫安都在同一個巷子遇到一位行為怪異的中年男子。高紫寧被對方騎腳踏車追上並不斷逼近；高紫安則是被對方「封路」，嚇得只能趕緊離開。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2443/d2443367.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2443%2Fd2443367.jpg&h=e6de6238&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲高紫寧（左）與姊姊高紫安都是表特版常客。（圖／校盟影業提供）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wXXvJ0zc7oY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwXXvJ0zc7oY&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=f7b5f21a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wXXvJ0zc7oY</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://star.ettoday.net/news/900146\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F900146&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=3015481b\" target=\"_blank\">http://star.ettoday.net/news/900146</a>"},{"pid":"cba1fe488ab10fb6d8b00116d85d5ffd2aebe5d8","tid":194254,"uid":13638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T01:27:29.000Z","msg":"豬撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c5413e159ba83b41418f3779da76189d0eef29","tid":194254,"uid":53496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T01:28:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>豬撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2ac20cea87fc96601af81f7023959f9fd3a195","tid":194254,"uid":25099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T01:39:29.000Z","msg":"對眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bcc3a418b4bfc83debc3ad9fe3f0548528c4c34","tid":194254,"uid":3649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:24:57.000Z","msg":"個髮型想點....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df84801d0c21a4f5514eb5525a3499f8f0df39c1","tid":194254,"uid":2640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:25:57.000Z","msg":"我屌！"},{"pid":"5fda172e2d8553dd70b725206725e285575f9849","tid":194254,"uid":50579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:26:39.000Z","msg":"台藝大個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma